{"tid":2478384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：拜登會延續特朗普政策  重新興建圍牆","createTime":"2021-04-07T04:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T05:52:53.000Z","uid":227801,"like":93,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"cfca1c48d14661247b70a5dda84db8886dbb8108","tid":2478384,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9441641/Biden-wants-RESTART-construction-Trumps-border-wall-plug-gaps-DHS-head-Mayorkas-says.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-9441641%2FBiden-wants-RESTART-construction-Trumps-border-wall-plug-gaps-DHS-head-Mayorkas-says.html&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=19c6f889\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9441641/Biden-wants-RESTART-construction-Trumps-border-wall-plug-gaps-DHS-head-Mayorkas-says.html</a><br />\nJoe Biden&nbsp;is considering restarting construction on&nbsp;Donald Trump's southern border wall as his administration continues to grapple with a growing&nbsp;immigration&nbsp;crisis including record numbers of illegal crossers.<br />\nHomeland Security Secretary Alejandro Mayorkas told employees, according to the&nbsp;Washington Times, that construction might resume to plug 'gaps' in the current barrier between the U.S. and Mexico.<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/dhs-alejandro-mayorkas-border-wall-b1827535.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fus-politics%2Fdhs-alejandro-mayorkas-border-wall-b1827535.html&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=03873830\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/dhs-alejandro-mayorkas-border-wall-b1827535.html</a><br />\nCons